                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>{formatDate(user.lastOrder)}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        {subscriberEmails.has(user.email) ? (
                                            <span class="status-badge subscribed">
                                                ‚úì Suscrito
                                            </span>
                                        ) : (
